talyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/BuildIt-logo2-300x83.png 300w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/BuildIt-logo2-768x211.png 768w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/BuildIt-logo2-600x165.png 600w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/BuildIt-logo2.png 1523w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-fa2ad33\" data-id=\"fa2ad33\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a41e4db elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a41e4db\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>SPAR SA understands that youth employment is important for our country\u2019s economic growth. As such, SPAR has collaborated with YES for Youth to create a quality work experience to enable youth to reach their full career potential.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>As\u00a0the implementation partner for the SPAR Group&#8217;s YES for Youth program since 2019, Catalyx has empowered and placed over 450 youth per year into SPAR and Build It stores nationally.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3c43381 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"3c43381\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4539c25 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4539c25\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">ABSA\u2019S READY TO WORK PROGRAMME<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-08e83ab elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"08e83ab\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5349 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/ABSA_Group_Limited_Logo-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"123\" height=\"123\" srcset=\"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/ABSA_Group_Limited_Logo-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/ABSA_Group_Limited_Logo-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/ABSA_Group_Limited_Logo-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/ABSA_Group_Limited_Logo-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/ABSA_Group_Limited_Logo-600x600.png 600w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/ABSA_Group_Limited_Logo-100x100.png 100w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/ABSA_Group_Limited_Logo.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 123px) 100vw, 123px\" \/><\/p><p>Absa Bank Limited launched its ReadyToWork Programme in 2016, which focuses on training, capacity building and placements. Catalyx was tasked to deliver this programme in various communities nationally. Absa\u2019s ReadyToWork Programme provides a valuable bridge between the worlds of school, college or university and that of work. This job preparation initiative enables school leavers and college or university graduates to explore and develop the skills required for a successful transition into employment or self-employment.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>With ReadyToWork (R2W), Catalyx trained 12 500 candidates in all provinces across SA within 18 months. Of those trained, Catalyx facilitated employment opportunities for over 10 500 and approximately 5 000 were offered employment. The R2W program was implemented in mostly the same towns and cities across SA as the JumpStart program. Some key employer partners included Bidvest, KFC, Tsebo Group, Clicks Group &amp; Victoria International.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cbea9fd elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"cbea9fd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c93083e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c93083e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">NYDA PROGRAMMES<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4029bb4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4029bb4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\u00a0<\/p><p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-5352 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/NYDA-Logo-300x190.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"114\" srcset=\"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/NYDA-Logo-300x190.jpg 300w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/NYDA-Logo-768x487.jpg 768w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/NYDA-Logo-600x380.jpg 600w, https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/NYDA-Logo.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 180px) 100vw, 180px\" \/>Catalyx has been responsible for managing and implementing the Expanded Public Works Programme (EPWP) facilitated by the National Youth Development Agency (NYDA).<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>This project provided unemployed youth with 6 \u2013 9 month work opportunities with participating non-profit organizations. All candidates completed the Life Skills Work Readiness Program in preparation for the workplace.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Catalyx coordinated this project for over 30 not for profit organizations who hosted 400 candidates in 2014\/15, 500 in 2015\/16 and 650 in 2016\/17.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Youth Programmes The YESFORYOUTH PROGRAMME is an initiative of the President, Cyril Ramaphosa, announced in 2018 as one of the ways in which South Africa\u2019s youth unemployment problem may be addressed. It is supported by numerous large companies in the country which have undertaken to provide youth with work experience for a period of 12-months [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":4890,"menu_order":0,"template":"elementor_header_footer","portfolio_category":[48],"class_list":["post-5238","portfolio","type-portfolio","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","portfolio_category-web-design"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/portfolio\/5238"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/portfolio"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/portfolio"}],"version-history":[{"count":29,"href":"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/portfolio\/5238\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5678,"href":"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/portfolio\/5238\/revisions\/5678"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4890"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5238"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"portfolio_category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/catalyx.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/portfolio_category?post=5238"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}